eading_number">8.</span> <span class="heading_text">FAQs about opening Singapore bank accounts</span></h2><div data-rlta-element="container" data-rlta-state="initial" data-rlta-id="2" data-rlta-type="accordions" data-rlta-title-tag="div" data-rlta-orientation="vertical" data-rlta-wrap-buttons="false" data-rlta-remember-active="false" data-rlta-theme="neutral" data-rlta-color-panels="false" data-rlta-positioning="top" data-rlta-alignment="left" data-rlta-has-button-scroller="false"><div id="rlta-can-foreigners-open-a-bank-account-in-singapore" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-can-foreigners-open-a-bank-account-in-singapore" aria-expanded="true" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="can-foreigners-open-a-bank-account-in-singapore" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="open"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> Can foreigners open a bank account in Singapore?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-can-foreigners-open-a-bank-account-in-singapore" aria-labelledby="rlta-can-foreigners-open-a-bank-account-in-singapore" tabindex="-1" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="open" data-rlta-color="false"><div data-rlta-element="panel-content"><p>Yes, foreigners, no matter their nationalty (except for the sanctioned list) can open bank accounts in Singapore <strong>with a valid passport, proof of address, Singapore pass.Â </strong>The account holder must be <strong>at least 18 years old.</strong>Â </p></div></div><div id="rlta-what-is-the-minimum-deposit-to-open-a-bank-account-in-singapore" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-what-is-the-minimum-deposit-to-open-a-bank-account-in-singapore" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="what-is-the-minimum-deposit-to-open-a-bank-account-in-singapore" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> What is the minimum deposit to open a bank account in Singapore?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-what-is-the-minimum-deposit-to-open-a-bank-